divs: Sighting DetailsI got up to use the bathroom and noticed a light triangle in the distance, where there were no lights there earlier that morning. It stayed in the same place for about an hour. I noticed lost time, I saw it then it was gone and an hour had elapsed from the time I noticed it and left. The hour that lapsed only felt like a couple of seconds. It was a weird experience to encounter, especially in the woods.
